               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="bold">16 HOW SUPPLIED/STORAGE AND HANDLING</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Adapalene and benzoyl peroxide gel USP, 0.1% / 2.5% is white to very pale yellow in color and opaque in appearance, and is supplied as follows:<br/>
                     <br/>45 gram pump   NDC 21922-052-50<br/>
                     <br/>Storage and handling</paragraph>
                  <list listType="unordered" styleCode="Disc">
                     <item>Store at 20°C to 25°C (68°F to 77°F); excursions permitted to 15°C to 30°C (59°F to 86°F) [see USP Controlled Room Temperature].</item>
                     <item>Protect from light.</item>
                     <item>Keep out of reach of children.</item>
                     <item>Keep away from heat.</item>
                  </list>
